    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救下一首热门歌曲！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐是世界上最宝贵的财富，而装满未发行曲目的硬盘被一个想要垄断排行榜的团伙盗走。现在，就看你的了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/18d8403a10584abb284ae728e666c749.poster.avif?t=1751554859\" width=612 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/18d8403a10584abb284ae728e666c749.webm?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/18d8403a10584abb284ae728e666c749.mp4?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演蒂娜与特纳——她是街区最顶尖的逃脱司机，他是拥有完美射击准度的神枪手。这对搭档将凭借各自独特的天赋，在高强度任务中融合动作与节奏，与时间赛跑，拯救那份能震撼世界的艺术：音乐。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/00ddbdcd26d3ead86884d9869d4138e9.poster.avif?t=1751554859\" width=612 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/00ddbdcd26d3ead86884d9869d4138e9.webm?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/00ddbdcd26d3ead86884d9869d4138e9.mp4?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/3b782b2f6cc0a4aea42f8b450f161888.poster.avif?t=1751554859\" width=612 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/3b782b2f6cc0a4aea42f8b450f161888.webm?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795630/extras/3b782b2f6cc0a4aea42f8b450f161888.mp4?t=1751554859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核心特色：  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    以驾驶与枪战为核心的快节奏游戏玩法  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    充满都市风格的鲜明视觉效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    说唱歌手NP Vocal创作的原创配乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    充满魅力的角色与受街头文化启发的剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    充满动作、追逐与音乐挑战的任务</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
